款數字節節上升！"},{"pid":"36e861d2e1885332506e0e674d31e276ec5acd3c","tid":279740,"uid":115516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"回水<br />\n<br />\n仲有個30萬咩料射左落海，蟲太似乎想側側膊冇件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a6f6d424f1b251ea5ba078332e96ac78ffcbad","tid":279740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回水<br />\n<br />\n仲有個30萬咩料射左落海，蟲太似乎想側側膊冇件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n四眼疏忽射左30萬落海究竟係乜柒事？<br />\n(夠陳云叫雞叫到精盡人亡)<br />\n<br />\n等熱血離教者去神駒爆料<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673ee7ed908fc99e00f982d5416e5c5efa132568","tid":279740,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06ba2413571c52fb989f60e24205385c118d204","tid":279740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"水泥隊話要REFUND本民青捐款:<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6734478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6734478&d=xdvyTn8elpyOrQjx963uTMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=05662f1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6734478</a><br />\n<br />\n證明PAYPAL REFUND熱血課金真係有效<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續廣傳, 加油！<br />\n<br />\n水泥隊就快死啦！"},{"pid":"8aa1d6d7fe7cedcab1e70b992bf3c369ed02bc9b","tid":279740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水泥隊話要REFUND本民青捐款:<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6734478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6734478&d=xdvyTn8elpyOrQjx963uTMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=05662f1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6734478</a><br />\n<br />\n證明PAYPAL REFUND熱血課金真係有效<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續廣傳, 加油！<br />\n<br />\n水泥隊就快死啦！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水泥隊依家驚到瀨屎<br />\n可能尋晚比鳩達屌足一粒鐘！<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6737967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6737967&d=xdvyTn8elpyOrQjx963uTMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=33ea2c9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6737967</a>"},{"pid":"79166423ecde4671eedb3038d78253c693054682","tid":279740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>狗主死忠教路 退課金「餓死狗」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2017/06/15/a14c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2Fa14c.jpg&h=78fbcf50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其鍵盤打嘴炮，不如斷人衣食更實際。有「狗主」支持者教路，通過PayPal（PP）捐款予「熱狗」者，可在捐款的180天內要求退款，更截圖展示有人取回課金的電郵。「無敵神駒」仇思達就在其fb「大力推介」，呼籲「苦主」退款。有人則提到，倘覺得受「熱狗」所騙，可考慮到小額錢債審裁處提出索償。<br />\n<br />\n在高登討論區，「焦土力量」以「180日內PAYPAL課金『熱血公民』可以禁制要求回水」，文中引用了PayPal的退款政策，又指若要提交退款申請，「請在退回物品後的30天內登入你的PayPal賬戶，然後按一下『申請退貨運費賠償』，並提交表格及退貨證明。......回水最實際，一蚊不課『熱狗』賤。」<br />\n<br />\nPP捐款可縮 或入稟追數<br />\n<br />\n有網民就慨嘆「無物品可退」，有人就稱自己並非經PayPal捐款，有人則呻已超過申索期限。「Yasmin Miu」就在網上討論區留言「教路」，稱各「課金苦主」可向小額錢債審裁處提出申索，「For銀行過數或現金實付，有receipt可透過小額錢債追數，免律師、百幾蚊申請費。」<br />\n<br />\n仇思達「大力推介」網民通過PayPal要求退款。「Sunny Sun Yue」說：「『神駒』千祁（祈）唔好手軟......襯（趁）勢一路追擊，退錢真係可以攞囥R㗎！無錢......唔通佢會養住班賤狗仔咩？到時一定狗咬狗骨！」<br />\n<br />\n「李絲絲」揶揄道：「 人地（哋）大台一集都籌到八萬（元）啦，捐一千（元）咁少當人地（哋）乞衣（兒）咩，快啲攞番（返）走晒啦！唔希（稀）罕你啲錢呀！」<br />\n<br />\n「Tai Man Chan」建議，「各位益友，可以先課金一舊（嚿）水俾（畀）佢地（哋），響個『課金光環』打 『老師又......中』或者『老師早安』，然後申請退款，諗起都好玩。」「Castor Ho」認為，「但咁樣可能算係『貨物已交付』（冇得退款）。」仇思達就回應，「玩佢都費事啦，唔好益佢收視。」<br />\n<br />\n「Dominic Chien」就擔心，「呢次算斷人衣食，趕狗入窮行（巷）。呢班咁Short嘅人，好難講，......如果退款後有任何安全問題，記得報警求助，相信警方今次會非常落力去幫你。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，「熱城」支持者「Edward Ho」就提出「以彼之道還施彼身」，稱「我忽然諗起，我之前都有用paypal交月費俾（畀）老人家（狗主）個MyRadio架（㗎）喎......」<br />\n<br />\n「熱狗」倡同一招數還拖<br />\n<br />\n「Jase Chiu」曲線留言：「你地（哋）千祈千祈唔好要求退款arrrrrrrrrrrr」「李瑞欣」稱，「賣台（MyRadio）今鋪大獲（鑊），如果城&times;論壇果（嗰）堆人跟你個（嗰）招叫賣台回水，賣台要硬食......」「Takeshi Chan」更揶揄道：「嗱，退還退，唔好要招牌節目退款呀，老人家好要面嘎（㗎）。」 ■香港文匯報記者 羅旦"},{"pid":"d52e969fd97c07f84870269b914c6b55266e29a8","tid":279740,"uid":66124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"第五個成功例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/wRrku8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FwRrku8.jpg&h=3d85ef35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d60f5f9f8fb6cd85a8b19253a9a5f20da0db988d","tid":279740,"uid":17265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:31:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1db800f3ee97215e7227d74a0caec05cae9a9cc","tid":279740,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T23:55:43.000Z","msg":"咁多水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7617757c0ace413bd6ee98b7f1f39099732e80eb","tid":279740,"uid":17265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第五個成功例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/wRrku8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FwRrku8.jpg&h=3d85ef35&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}